&lt;p&gt;&lt;iframe src=&#34;http://www.slideshare.net/slideshow/embed_code/15327269&#34; width=&#34;342&#34; height=&#34;291&#34; frameborder=&#34;0&#34; marginwidth=&#34;0&#34; marginheight=&#34;0&#34; scrolling=&#34;no&#34; style=&#34;border:1px solid #CCC;border-width:1px 1px 0;margin-bottom:5px&#34; allowfullscreen webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen&gt; &lt;/iframe&gt; &lt;div style=&#34;margin-bottom:5px&#34;&gt; &lt;strong&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.slideshare.net/s_kozake/ss-15327269&#34; title=&#34;たのしい高階関数&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;たのしい高階関数&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/strong&gt; from &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://www.slideshare.net/s_kozake&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;信一 小酒&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

